      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm working on this paper about language in professional spaces and i'm stuck on something. if i had to choose between these two styles for a formal research submission, which one sounds more \"intellectually rigorous\" and professional?\n\nSample A: The socio-economic implications of urban development are multifaceted, necessitating a nuanced approach to policy implementation that accounts for historical disparities in resource allocation.\n\nSample B: When u look at how cities grow, it really affects how ppl live and get what they need, especially since some neighborhoods been left behind for a long time, so the policies gotta be real careful about that.\n\nwhich one would an academic reviewer take more seriously?",
